{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1772915875195,"sessionID":"ses_335fe82edffegf3xUTqYmkHwvH","part":{"id":"prt_cca055d71001l2Kkp3rQY4501m","sessionID":"ses_335fe82edffegf3xUTqYmkHwvH","messageID":"msg_cca05221a001MkJ1HEavRTVN2Z","type":"tool","callID":"call_F0I8Gxfvxs12HDYs2ZJVrvIS","tool":"write","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# Simple Local File Organizer\n\nA command-line utility that automatically organizes files in a directory into categorized folders based on file type.\n\n## Features\n\n- Automatically organize files into categories (Images, Documents, Videos, Archives, Audio, Code, Other)\n- Preview actions with dry-run mode\n- Simple command-line interface\n- Fast execution for large directories\n- Local-only operation (no external services)\n\n## Installation\n\n```bash\npip install -e .\n```\n\nOr run directly:\n\n```bash\npython main.py\n```\n\n## Usage\n\n### Organize a directory\n\n```bash\nfile-organizer organize ~/Downloads\n```\n\n### Preview before organizing\n\n```bash\nfile-organizer organize ~/Downloads --dry-run\n```\n\n## Categories\n\nFiles are organized into the following categories:\n\n- **Images**: .jpg, .jpeg, .png, .gif, .bmp, .svg, .webp, .tiff\n- **Documents**: .pdf, .docx, .doc, .txt, .rtf, .xlsx, .xls, .pptx, .ppt, .odt, .odp\n- **Videos**: .mp4, .mov, .avi, .mkv, .flv, .wmv, .webm\n- **Archives**: .zip, .tar, .gz, .rar, .7z, .bz2, .xz\n- **Audio**: .mp3, .wav, .flac, .aac, .ogg, .wma, .m4a\n- **Code**: .py, .js, .html, .css, .java, .c, .cpp, .h, .hpp, .rb, .php, .go, .rs, .ts\n- **Other**: Any file not matching known categories\n\n## Project Structure\n\n```\nfile-organizer/\n├── main.py        # CLI entry point\n├── organizer.py   # Core organization logic\n├── file_types.py  # File type mappings\n├── utils.py       # Utility functions\n└── setup.py       # Installation configuration\n```\n\n## License\n\nMIT License\n","filePath":"/private/tmp/opencode-serve-test/README.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","title":"README.md","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/private/tmp/opencode-serve-test/README.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"time":{"start":1772915875186,"end":1772915875194}}}}
